WEBVTT

00:11:28.903 --> 00:11:31.577
And yet, here you are,
in a very different place today.

00:11:31.601 --> 00:11:35.375
What advice would you give
Mark Zuckerberg?

00:11:35.399 --> 00:11:39.228
Some steps that he could take
that might start to --

00:11:39.252 --> 00:11:43.431
A, first of all, most fundamentally,
improve, tackle the problem directly.

00:11:43.455 --> 00:11:45.159
And then perhaps, more indirectly,

00:11:45.183 --> 00:11:48.772
you know, change how he might be
regarded going forward?

00:11:49.704 --> 00:11:52.787
BG: I think it's a huge challenge,

00:11:52.811 --> 00:11:56.989
because a lot of the ills
of this period now

00:11:57.013 --> 00:11:59.664
are being heaped onto, OK ...